var checkedImages=[],API="/repo/delete/";function deleteImage(e){$.get(API+getImageName()+"/"+e)}function getImageName(){return $(".breadcrumb li.active").text()}function toggleDeleteButton(e){if(e){var t=$('<input id="delete-button" type="button" value="Delete Selected" style="position: absolute;right: 15px;top: 10px;padding: 10px;border-radius: 5px;color: #3379b7;"/>');t.appendTo($("dl")),t.click(function(){confirm("Are you sure you want to delete selected images?")&&$.each(checkedImages,function(e,t){deleteImage(t),e==checkedImages.length-1&&location.reload()})})}else $("#delete-button").remove()}function addCheckboxes(){var e=$("#main");e.find("thead tr").prepend("<th></th>"),e.find("tbody tr").prepend('<td><input type="checkbox"></td>'),$("#main :checkbox").change(function(){var e=$(this).parent().parent().find("td:nth-child(3)").text();this.checked?(checkedImages.length||toggleDeleteButton(!0),checkedImages.push(e)):(checkedImages.splice(checkedImages.indexOf(e),1),checkedImages.length||toggleDeleteButton(!1))})}addCheckboxes();